title: Wiltshire YouTube star Zoella made into waxwork
text:
Madame Tussauds' waxwork version of Zoella Credit: Madame Tussauds/Ode Wiltshire YouTube star Zoella has been unveiled as a waxwork at Madame Tussauds in London. Zoella, born Zoe Sugg in Lacock, started her fashion and lifestyle blog six years ago. It's since received more than half a billion hits.
Her debut novel Girl Online has become a best-seller. More details here.
Last updated Mon 5 Oct 2015 Entertainment Wiltshire
